channel.title: Pi Help
channel.description: I am new to Java, and I want to know why whenever I try to load the run server on the client, the window just pops up saying press any key to continue, but the client doesn't load. Any help would be appreciated :)

item.title: Pi Help
item.dc:creator: @Jayden2 Jayden.
item.description:
@Jayden2 wrote:

Cosidering you are new I will tell you. It is because you have not changed the code of the compiler or Run. You could do you by right clicking it and pressing Edit.

You will see a code like the following:

Make the jdk1.6.0_(Your Version).

You can find the version you are currently using at.
C:\Program Files\Java.

Hope I helped.
